issue.title: Download and Transform Syracuse crime data to include (lon, lat) data
issue.body: It looks as though Syracuse's Open Data does not include longitude and latitude data in [their crime data](http://data.syrgov.net/datasets/weekly-part-1-crime-offenses-2018/data?selectedAttribute=Arrest). I will address this by using [mediagis/nominatim-docker](https://github.com/mediagis/nominatim-docker) to geocode the addresses specified.

issue.body: update `loadBuffaloData.py` to load other cities' data.
